\ncelebration at the Cuban Clul\nHe made the flight April 17, 191;\nThe Overseas Highway celt\nbration committee today issue\na call for donations of potter\nplants for the committee's offic\nin the La Concha Hotel. Warre\nSmith, chairman, said many v\nsitors are expected and a sui\nable tropical atmosphere is de\nsirable.\nMay 16, 1948\n\nSunday, No Paper\nconstruction a boost. For mm\nthing, in the first four months 0\nthis year they sold a record thre\nbillion dollars worth of new secu\nrities.\nCO B 0\nPHARMACY\ninner of I leminu\nmid (<riniull Streets\nFree Delivery\nCY 6-8575\nI\nDrinfc...\naaM\u00dfal\nPoray Studio\nHOURS:\nI 10:00 A.M. to 7 P.M.\n404 SOUTHARD STREET\nPHONE CY 6-3088\nj\nPIERCE\nBROTHERS\n628 FLEMING\nPHILCO\nFactor y-Supervised\nService\nMnn. Sat., 9 A.M. 5:30 P-*\nCY 6-5922 CY 6-8511\nJ\nI SATURDAY EVENING\n00 Sports 130 Behind M l\n6:15 News, W\u2019ther 9:00 L. Welk\n6:30 Youth Atka 10:00 Billy Grl>\u00ab\n7:00 Sword of 10:30 Theatre\n7:30 Dick Clark 4. 11:00 News.\n1:00 Sunaet Ranch U. 15 Sports\nKey West 1600\nSATURDAY BVENIN\u00ab\n7:00 News l:M Hawaii\n7:05 Sat. Melodies 9:00 Show Mun'\n7:30 News 10.00 Ne\u00bb<\n7:33 Sat. Melodies 10:05 Music tilB\u00bb\nS:00 News 11:00 News\nS:O5 Sat. Bandstd. 11:44\n4:30 News 11:S5 Late N e\nFORMICA^\nand Plastic\nWALL TILE\nHIADQUARTERS\nKey West\nFloor Covering\n132 DUVAL STREET\nPHONE CY 6-2512^\nbroadcasting*\nDirect from Our Offi<\u00b0\nSutro Bros. Co\nMembers New York Stock Exd>\u00bb\u00ab*\n5:00 P.M. u<\nCLOSING QUOTATIONS\nWKWF","height":"29179","width":"19862"}}
